intentName: Text to Array of Observables v1.0.2
description:
Description: This Component takes in a string and uses the Swimlane Action iOC Parser to extract observables and their type from the string.

Inputs : an alert or email object which has been stringified.

Outputs : an array of simple Observables (value & type)

Configuration: No configuration is required for this component.
name: Filter - Parse Observables
